{"tid":867512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人發覺買唔到雙飛人","createTime":"2018-10-18T17:12:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T06:19:02.000Z","uid":196652,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a4748880df45aefb74fe9eba775fc4aa81c4e63f","tid":867512,"uid":196652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"話說有蚊咬，想買支雙飛人搽，點知葯房話冇貨。<br />\n咁我咪去萬寧，都冇。<br />\n再去惠康，又冇，佢仲問我呢排咩事，咁多人問雙飛人，一日幾個人問。<br />\n<br />\n平時覺得雙飛人唔係一樣難買到嘅葯水，所以覺得有啲奇怪。"},{"pid":"5b556a6bcd7e0042dffb5bec253cfdb6ddec4106","tid":867512,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"去沙田行轉"},{"pid":"6f440e055d8aeab4552103a7fe76fc746f36c32f","tid":867512,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b556a6bcd7e0042dffb5bec253cfdb6ddec4106","tid":867512,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"去沙田行轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"就知"},{"pid":"02d50e1fd6d67f0c5236cbc7e8cf64188a4c88d1","tid":867512,"uid":46584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:16:12.000Z","msg":"打緊貿易戰啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfcbc3ebf4ab4582fc29ec558670592c46ed149","tid":867512,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T17:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似炒貴咗成倍"},{"pid":"ec7b0cd928435d8761cfedeace91f2c62288969d","tid":867512,"uid":155509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"早排轉廠呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8b488c4d9e870507548c31d9231fa27f1f63c9","tid":867512,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:14:56.000Z","msg":"簡體?"},{"pid":"695517e89f10f08d36de026db30413abb479dc53","tid":867512,"uid":42865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,